water_monitor = DataFlowTracker()
fire_monitor = SecurityEnergyMonitor()
air_monitor = StrategicAnalytics()

# Create elemental scoring system
elemental_scorer = ElementalScorer(
    earth_weight=0.25,
    water_weight=0.25, 
    fire_weight=0.25,
    air_weight=0.25
)
```

Phase 2: Eagle Eye Integration (Months 4-6)

```python
# Build Eagle Eye observation framework
eagle_eye = EagleEye(
    triad_system=existing_triad,
    elemental_monitors=[earth_monitor, water_monitor, fire_monitor, air_monitor],
    memory_system=QuintessentialMemory()
)

# Implement strategic oversight
strategic_planner = ElementalStrategicPlanner(eagle_eye)
```

Phase 3: Quintessential Synthesis (Months 7-12)

```python
# Create the complete integrated system
quintessential_system = QuintessentialAI(
    triad=triad_ai,
    eagle_eye=eagle_eye,
    elemental_governance=ElementalGovernance(),
    feedback_loop=ElementalFeedbackLoop()
)

# Implement emergent intelligence
emergent_intelligence = EmergentQuintessenceDetector(quintessential_system)
```

